title: 1933–34 Tranmere Rovers F.C. season
text: <a href="Tranmere%20Rovers%20F.C.">Tranmere Rovers F.C.</a> played the 1933–34 season in the <a href="Football%20League%20Third%20Division%20North">Football League Third Division North</a>. It was their 13th season of league <a href="Association%20football">football</a>, and they finished 7th of 22. They reached the Fourth Round of the <a href="FA%20Cup">FA Cup</a>.
